Class       (template, blueprint)   => Properties, methods (functions)
Object                              => state, behavior
Inheritance                         => parent - child
Polymorphism                        => လုပ်တဲ့ အလုပ်တူ၊ ပြုလုပ်နည်း မတူ
Abstraction                         => လိုအပ်တာတွေပြ၊ မလိုအပ်တာတွေ hide ထား
Encapsulation                       => ထိန်းချုပ်ထား...

Properties    => global variables   => data member, field, state, instance
Global variable                     => methods တွေ ရဲ့အပြင်မှာရေးထားတဲ့ variable
                                    => static variable
                                    => non-static variable || instance variable

Methods
    Method Syntax : <return type> <method name>() { <implementation> }
    Return Types - primitive datatype, non-primitive datatype
    No-return type - void

    Method Type by OOP
       1. instance method (non-static method)
       2. static method

Method Signature
    1. Return type ပါ
    2. Return type မပါ
    3. Parameter ပါ
    4. Parameter မပါ

Object Creation
    CN obj = new CN(); obj object
    new CN(); anonymous object

Properties Initialization
    1. direct reference
    2. by method
    3. by constructor

Access Modifier
    1. public       - in use : properties, methods, class   // accessible range - the whole project
    2. protected    - in use : properties, methods          // accessible range - same class and child class
    3. private      - in use : properties, methods          // accessible range - same class
    4. default      - in use : properties, methods, class   // accessible range - same class and same package

Non-access Modifier
    1. static
    2. final
    3. synchronized
    4. transient
    5. abstract

Method Syntax
    min : <return type> <method name>() { }
    max : <access modifier> <non-access modifier> <return type> <method name>( <parameter> ) { }

Constructor
    1. Default constructor (zero argument constructor)
    2. Parameterized constructor

    syntax : <class name>( <parameter> ) { <implementation> }

    Access Modifiers in constructor (usually) : public, private, default

    note : Class တစ်ခုမှာ Default Constructor တစ်ခုအမြဲပါ။
    Default Constructor : <class name>() {}

Initializer Block
    1. instance initializer block
    2. static initializer block


Lesson-5 Inheritance
    1. Single inheritance
    2. Multi-level Inheritance
    3. Hierarchical Inheritance
    4. Multiple Inheritance
    5. Hybrid Inheritance

Chapter-6 Polymorphism
    ဦးတည်ချက်တူ လုပ်ဆောင်ချက်မတူ
    1. Method Overloading
    2. Method Overriding